reviewText: It was good just too bad I live in the usa. Because of the region thing ...
LOVE IT!!!! I'm a huge skins fan, and it's all here in THIS box set! This is a must have for sure!!!

What an experience. Great acting, great stories, plus great music. This was a series you did not want to end. Series 1 thru 4, and 7 were great series 5 and 6 were okay. Anybody who watches this series will never forget Effe, Naomi, and Emily. I'm glad I bought that DVDs, the extras are great too.

I love this series. I'm from America and had to purchase a region free dvd player, which I have no problem with. But, I received 2 series 5 dvds, and am missing series 2. I'm quite upset because series 2 was one of my favorites.
Great set. Love it. Wish I had got it two years ago. Watched it over and over again. Love the seller too. Very helpful, I buy from them again.
A must-have collection if your a Skins fan.
